      public Car createCar(String[][] carToBuyData, String[][] data, Finder f)
      This method creates a Car object based on the provided car data. It uses a switch/case to generate the car object based on the "Car Type". At the moment it seems a bit redundant, but a better way to input all necessary data automatically is not available.
      Parameters:
      carToBuyData - the data of the car to buy
      data - the data of all cars
      f - the Finder object to find data in the 2D array
      Returns:
      a Car object representing the car to buy
